n\n\n2. He goes to school ________ bike.\n\nA. on \tB. for \tC. in \tD. by\n\n表示乘坐某种交通工具，介词用 by，这题选 D。\n\n## 注意","excerpt":"","includedFiles":[],"tasklistId":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"考点判断","slug":"考点判断","link":"#考点判断","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"思路总结","slug":"思路总结","link":"#思路总结","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"注意","slug":"注意","link":"#注意","children":[]}]}}
